Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.77,0:00:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  月水木
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.82,0:00:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始穿夏季校服了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你很相稱哦  月水木
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.93,0:00:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  月水木
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏季校服和你很相稱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.71,0:00:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  月水木
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好像會變得很熱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到大家穿著夏季校服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能感覺到季節變化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有某個人一年四季都穿著白大褂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無變化
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  實際上…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:54.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}羊毛  100%
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:56.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}滌綸  80%    羊毛  20%
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面料啊  居然變薄了喲！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御同學  伊御同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏季制服殺必死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真宵同學  剛才那個實在是有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御君嬌羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御君  原來你會嬌羞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真能說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:44.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,330)}只是被突然襲擊嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是打掃泳池的絕好天氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託先準備好了的人開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:03.86,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御庭把頭髮紮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為好像會弄濕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御庭  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要不要去留個長髮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果佳奈留長髮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體積…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變得很大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是重了點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會那樣啦  而且一點都不可愛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  如果可以的話就請用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這樣溫柔的學生  老師好高興的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給您防曬霜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給您太陽鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好開心…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你冰敷巾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種擔心我才不開心的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:14.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,430)}謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真宵  你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木同學  給你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.03,0:05:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要綁成兩頭刷子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個咕嚕嚕地轉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,污漬就一網打盡了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的是的  就這樣連續轉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日大家的「脖梗」都好閃耀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是夏日的「陽光」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夏日裏的健康美的照耀下  眼睛不知不覺就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不是不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是「脖梗」我無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為京谷的視線只鎖定了崎守了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確定了目標就不要放開視線哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會被華麗且優雅地躲過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個誤會要何時才能解開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說音無你會注意看妹子們的哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是笑容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京谷因為伊御的回答而覺得自己是骯髒的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是說「胸部」會好一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不勞您費神了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然到處都是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水蚤和青蛙這裏那裏都有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用水沖掉有點那什麼  怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工具室裏不是有水槽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:22.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}惡搞青蛙軍曹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那水蚤就放到水槽裏  軍曹就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍曹你個頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒鹽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溶掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:32.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是蛞蝓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  用掃帚打曲棍球啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  掃帚同…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  榊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掃帚同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一點就特升兩階了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:55.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}士兵戰死官升2階
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒嘿  抱歉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:07:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掃帚同學嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說這個就變成榊同學了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定了  那麼這個掃帚就命名為榊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是「足球就是朋友」一樣的設定呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠對那位「朋友」毫不猶豫地頭頂腳踢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說對朋友不用客氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在說…掃帚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊君  我要用刷子打你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要摧殘我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是針對你  是掃帚才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只聽台詞  就像是我的危機啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.52,0:08:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  就算是假設  好歹也是朋友的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我猶豫一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊君  覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊  你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要全力上了哦  榊君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊  去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要一個個都念名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  大家  你們欺負榊過頭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像過去也有過這種對話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就相信你會幫我制止的  摯友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  掃帚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是榊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬  沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個水桶要放在哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:10:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然頭部被水和撞擊還有黑暗攻擊了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從背後來了重重一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是姬和御庭友情的雙重攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木也沒受傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還真是萬幸  要是水桶倒過來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會變成西原和榊那樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:27.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,300)}水池掃除結束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給大家準備了冰激淩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事的說？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個要怎麼辦  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮起來了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在那裏冰著的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:53.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1030,150)}切好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:56.36,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰激淩也冰冰的好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來吃片西瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜放點鹽就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  榊去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你掉在這個池子裏的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金色的榊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是銀色的榊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  我怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是普通的榊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要不要大家來辦個學習會呀  為了明天的考試
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要參加嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那地點就定在伊御同學家裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去我家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然月水木也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天HACHIPOCHI的打工輪到我的班了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.92,0:11:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  打工加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  大家加油學習
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見咯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家各自回家以後馬上準備下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  上戰場了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰場？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要給敵人收拾房間的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是學習會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:21.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,300)}好了  上戰場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:23.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1040,370)}伊御的公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨  月水木  你好快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打…打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去端茶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人在…伊御的房間裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「想要搜房間的話  伊御不在的此刻正是個好機會哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不可以做這樣的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要搜房間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:14.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,120)}伊御的襯衫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木同學…你在做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了消除你們的記憶  要讓你們的腦袋…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受強力的衝擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦袋…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:14:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我們不會對伊御君說的  月水木同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御同學的襯衫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真宵同學你是在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在太陽的味道裏還夾雜著伊御同學的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  下面到小姬了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這種事我可幹不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了別客氣  請便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:21.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}雖然很想吐槽  但是對自己吐槽又做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼說都太害羞了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿著人家的襯衫做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:33.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}各種騷亂之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:33.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}學習會開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的我就當沒看到了  快把筆記打開吧  真宵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K.O. PERFECT！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開玩笑的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:14:59.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了給我乖乖坐下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊…伊御同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很不好意思來著…把教科書借給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:08.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(80,300)}忘\N帶\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說「學習會」的是這張嘴巴吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好  臉蛋可以被…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:18.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,260)}學習中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你可以教我做這題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是年級裏成績最好的班級
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏呢是這樣做的  明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我不懂  我太沒出息了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是解出問題答案的話人家是不會明白的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木同學  不用那麼失落啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有失落呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏使用上公式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣子的話就很容易解出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:05.08,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣氛不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木同學  吃醋…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下手太重啦  月水木同學  好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼  真宵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到伊御同學和小姬在一起  月水木同學吃醋…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木同學  我的大腿忍不住這疼痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你從剛才開始就慘叫什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我來腳（教）…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新來過了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:17:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣考試就沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  大家暑假一起去旅遊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的啊  旅遊什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅遊嗎  說起來之前和榊他們一起去的那個出租別墅就不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽上去似乎很好玩的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出租別墅嗎  我第一次參加的說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們快去預定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真性急呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等考試考完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和伊御一起旅遊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:46.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(990,110)}考試結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家考得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和原來差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒什麼自信呢  不過這次有和大家參加了學習會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:17:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒什麼問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呢  只要想起在伊御家學到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要想起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能想起襯衫的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白癡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:20.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1030,400)}午休
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來今天天氣預報說下午會下雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種大晴天？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種季節天氣變化很快的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你帶傘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  帶了  我可有好好準備過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把它忘在家裏的桌子上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是忘記了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意不要忘記東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼在這個感覺馬上要下暴雨的日子裏  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一個劃時代的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:19:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是什麼奇怪的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是對於熱戀中的情侶來說是絕對值得推薦的一個玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的一個心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:13.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,560)}小孔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個裝在傘頭上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣  馬上變成了真正的合撐傘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原…原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是滅火道具一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  月水木同學給你用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.74,0:19:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的開始下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已經到了梅雨季節了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅雨…6月
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六月新娘也到來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子對這種事果然還是很在意？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很在…意…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NOW！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.83,0:19:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NOW？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:19:58.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1000,460)}放學時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得準備了把傘  結果卻忘在了桌子上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我準備了兩把備傘喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有把備傘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒帶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那月水木要和我一起撐傘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家是一個方向的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說翻譯過來就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起撐傘好害羞的  我很想拒絕  但是心裏很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原…原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的傘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  我準備了兩把看來有用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你有意準備的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傘原來還能飛的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會飛的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我震驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛出去的傘  要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是  我去回收吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊…榊同學！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.45,0:21:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝照顧了  朋友們…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼伊御同學  月水木同學  明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的道路  因為空中的雨滴而濕透的純白襯衫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.22,0:21:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會淋濕的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊貼在薄薄的面料上的雪白的肌膚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把傘撐好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由雨音編織的包容而自然的BGM
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然地這是發什麼病…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以嘛  請小心送你回家的狼哦 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我會被襲擊嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.42,0:21:58.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}害\N羞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.60,0:22:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非我被偷襲了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋…
